==English==

===Etymology===
{{Ger.}} ''bumboot'', "ship's boat".<br/>
{{D.}} ''bomschuit'', "small fishing boat". {{D.}} ''bom'' + ''schuit'', "boat" + "ship".

===Noun===
'''bumboat'''
#{{nautical}} a small [[boat]] used for carrying [[provisions]] to [[ship]]s lying at [[anchor]] in a [[harbour]]